Naming Conventions:
			We will use the naming convention just like JAVA.
			Variables	:	lowerCamelCase
			Classes		:	UpperCamelCase
			Methods		:	lowerCamelCase
			Constants	:	UPPERCASE_SEPARATED_BY_UNDERSCORE



Indent Style:
			Indent Style	:	Allman Style ( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indent_style#Allman_style )
			Indent Space	:	1TBS
			
			/*
			 * For example : 
			 * Something like this.
			 */

			if(x==1)
			{			
				while (x == y)
				{
  		 			something();
  					somethingelse();
				}
			}



Commenting:
			We will follow the usual commenting style of JAVA and HTML.



Spacing:
			We will use "Linux kernel style" for use of spaces mostly.




